snippet.title: Garden of Seif: Chronicles of an Assassin | OPENING VIDEO
snippet.description:
A dark fantasy visual novel with an epic story and villain love interests. Be a villain. Date villains.

https://foxdriftstudios.carrd.co/
STEAM: https://bit.ly/3CVf5v1
DEMO: https://foxdrift-studios.itch.io/garden-of-seif
KICKSTARTER: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/garden-of-seif/garden-of-seif-chronicles-of-an-assassin

Synopsis:
An undercover assassin is on a mission to knock out her marks, but things turn upside down when a guild of enemy assassins is after her bounty. She runs into two mysterious men along her journey, both claiming to be trustworthy, but their secrets could lead her deeper into trouble.
